title: Did a Hiker Photograph a Ghost and Find Car Keys in the Woods?
subtitle: Viral postings tell the tale of a missing woman, a ghostly apparition, and an abandoned car in the middle of nowhere.
author: Jordan Liles
vclaim: After spotting a ghostly figure in a photo, the photographer returned to the location, found car keys that matched an abandoned vehicle, and learned that a woman had mysteriously disappeared nearby.
